description: [``botocore``] Add new parameters on RegisterUser and UpdateUser APIs to assign or update external ID associated to QuickSight users federated through web identity.
[``botocore``] Introduced FindingReasonCodes, PlatformDifferences, DiskResourceUtilization and NetworkResourceUtilization to GetRightsizingRecommendation action

[``botocore``] Adds support for 1) additional instance types, 2) additional instance metrics, 3) finding reasons for instance recommendations, and 4) platform differences between a current instance and a recommended instance type.
[``botocore``] This release adds support for creating and managing EC2 On-Demand Capacity Reservations on Outposts.
[``botocore``] This release provides dimensions and unit support for metric filters.
